items.title: With Dodgers in town, Nats push for NL's top mark
items.summary: Had you looked at the baseball calendar three weeks ago, this weekend's Dodgers-Nationals series in Washington would have been tabbed as a potential National League Championship Series preview, albeit a series itself with very little at stake.
